This commit adds support for the LeapIO
RAID controller. It supports RAID levels
0, 1, 5, 6, 10, 50, and 60, and works with
both SAS and SATA HDDs/SSDs.

Signed-off-by: doubled <doubled@leap-io-kernel.com>
